import React from 'react'
import { AppBar , Toolbar , IconButton } from '@mui/material'
import icon from '@mui/icons-material/'

export const muinav = () => {
  return (
    <AppBar position="static">
        <Toolbar>
            <IconButton>
                <icon />
            </IconButton>

        </Toolbar>

    </AppBar>
  )
}
